author: Brian Tracy
message: You can only grow if you're willing to feel awkward and uncomfortable when you try something new.
title: Thought of the day

author: Joan Didion
message: To free us from the expectations of others, to give us back to ourselves there lies the great, singular power of self-respect.
title: Thought of the day

author: Mabel Newcomber
message: It is more important to know where you are going than to get there quickly. Do not mistake activity for achievement.
title: Thought of the day

message: When you don't know what you believe, everything becomes an argument. Everything is debatable. But when you stand for something, decisions are obvious.
title: Thought of the day
